{"tid":1433163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世］黃嘉鍚律師樓 騙徒手法真係層出不窮","createTime":"2019-08-08T12:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T12:03:55.000Z","uid":125625,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8306e77e2ef52c0b01adc69879123bb4aba0a863","tid":1433163,"uid":125625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:01:30.000Z","msg":"代朋友po<br />\n<br />\n星期一，哥哥搵我，話佢朋友被捕，而且佢朋友媽媽俾人㬨，又搵唔倒自己個仔，唔知點算。我又幫吓手。<br />\n<br />\n後來，佢朋友保釋咗，不過我由哥哥打俾我開始就一直到不同電話騷擾，最多嘅喺23326195<br />\n<br />\n我打翻去，先知係<strong>黃嘉錫律師樓</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>我從來冇搵過呢個人</strong><br />\n<br />\n想再問清楚d，就話自己喺總機，咩都唔知；又係咁問我個人資料；我鳩答再block 鳩佢。 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5F0P0uT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5F0P0uT.jpg&h=089fc2c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SHJh9od.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSHJh9od.jpg&h=9a847972&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nopk69U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNopk69U.jpg&h=5b19f01e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbd38adee499e7cd80f49e9522a2c29563511ac7","tid":1433163,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:03:55.000Z","msg":"係咪得我一個睇唔出騙咗啲乜"}]}